Package org.miniauth.oauth.common

MiniAuth OAuth common classes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OAuthIncomingRequest
    Provider side request, which is sent by a client, for services that use OAuth.
    OAuthIncomingRequestBuilder
    Builds an OAuthIncomingRequest object.
    OAuthOutgoingRequest
    Client side request, which is being built by the client, for services that require OAuth.
    OAuthOutgoingRequestBuilder
    Builds an OAuthOutgoingRequest object.
    OAuthParamMap
    A "bean" class for encapsulating OAuth parameters.
    OAuthParamMapUtil
    Methods to extract OAuth params from the incoming/output partial request objects.
    OAuthRequestUtil
    OAuth incoming/outgoing request related utility methods.

Package org.miniauth.oauth.common Description

MiniAuth OAuth common classes. Note the package dependencies: core <- util <- common.
